<directions xmlns:php="http://php.net/xsl">&gt;
<step><![CDATA[Mix beef steak, ginger, sugar, dark soy sauce in a bowl, and let stand in the fridge for at least 20m]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[soak dried tangerine peel in hot water then drain for 20m]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[quickly stir fry the onions, then set aside in oil for 40s]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[quickly stir fry beef, then set aside for 90s]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Add oil then stir fry the tangerine peel, fresh chilies, szichuan pepper, and quickly set aside in oil for 90s]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Put onion and beef back in, add hoisin sauce, bean paste, light soy sauce for 40s]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Add the tangerine peel mix then serve for 20s]]></step>
&gt;</directions>
